How to configure and compile mgroms at IFREMER/CAPARMOR:
=======================================================
Intel compiler + Intel MPI

Environment:
-----------
module load intel-comp intel-mpi

Currently Loaded Modulefiles:
  1) intel-comp/2015.3.187         2) intel-mpi/5.0.3.048

Configuration and compilation:
-----------------------------
setenv MPI_INC /appli/intel/impi/5.0.3.048/intel64/include
setenv MPI_LIB /appli/intel/impi/5.0.3.048/intel64/lib

./configure --prefix=/home2/caparmor/grima/NH_Multigrid/IntelMPI --enable-intel_mpi [--enable-traceanalyser] [--enable-optimization=aggressive]
make clean
make 
make install

Submission:
----------
qsub run_mgroms_caparmor.pbs

Debugging with DDT:
------------------
module load ddt/4.2.2
ddt &